    match: Reframing

    docs do
      Reframing is an NLP technique that changes the meaning or context assigned to
      a situation without changing the facts. By shifting the frame, the same
      situation can produce entirely different emotional responses and behaviors.

      The "Six-Step Reframe" provides a complete process for identifying limiting
      frames and establishing more empowering alternatives.
    end docs

